name: Fortinet
description: Fortinet, Inc. provides cybersecurity and convergence of networking and security solutions worldwide. The company offers secure networking solutions that focus on the convergence of networking and security; network firewall solutions, which consist of FortiGate data centers, hyperscale, and distributed firewalls, as well as encrypted applications; wireless local area network (LAN) solutions; and secure connectivity solutions, including FortiSwitch secure ethernet switches, FortiAP wireless LAN access points, and FortiExtender 5G connectivity gateways.
